<item>
<title><![CDATA[Turning Data Into Decisions]]></title>
<link>https://example.com/?p=105</link>
<pubDate>Sun, 15 Mar 2026 09:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
<guid isPermaLink="false">https://example.com/?p=105</guid>
<description></description>
<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Most organisations are not short on data. They are short on decisions. Dashboards multiply, reports pile up, and yet the same questions keep coming back to the same meetings unanswered.</p>

<h2>Fewer metrics, chosen on purpose</h2>
<p>We help teams cut their reporting down to the handful of numbers that actually drive the business. When everyone watches the same few metrics, conversations get sharper and faster.</p>

<h2>Pair every number with an owner</h2>
<p>A metric without an owner is just trivia. We connect each key measure to a person and a decision it informs, so data leads to action instead of admiration.</p>

<p>Good analytics is not about collecting more, it is about deciding better. Start with the decision, then work backwards to the data you truly need.</p>]]></content:encoded>
<excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Most organisations are not short on data. They are short on decisions.]]></excerpt:encoded>
