<h2 style="text-align:center;">We help ambitious teams turn strategy into momentum</h2>
<p style="text-align:center;">Lumen Consulting partners with founders and leadership teams to sharpen their strategy, strengthen their brand, and ship the technology that moves the business forward.</p>

<h3>What we do</h3>
<p><strong>Strategy &amp; Growth</strong> &mdash; We help you find the few decisions that matter most and build a roadmap your whole team can rally behind.</p>
<p><strong>Brand &amp; Marketing</strong> &mdash; From positioning to launch, we shape a brand that earns attention and trust in a crowded market.</p>
<p><strong>Technology &amp; Delivery</strong> &mdash; We choose pragmatic technology and help your team ship it, without the buzzwords or the bloat.</p>

<h3>Why teams work with us</h3>
<p>We are a small, senior team. You work directly with the people doing the thinking, not a layer of account managers. We measure ourselves on outcomes, and we leave your team more capable than we found it.</p>

